OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe evening
OL,6,Fwill start dry, but cloud and rain
OL,7,Fwill soon spread east to all parts,
OL,8,Fturning heavier for a time overnight.
OL,9,FClearer spells and showers in
OL,10,Fnorthwest by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FAny remaining overnight rain
OL,13,Fwill soon clear east then sunny spells
OL,14,Fand showers. Drier for a time in the
OL,15,Fafternoon before further showers
OL,16,Flater, heavy at times. Cool and
OL,17,Fblustery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
